    "We summarize the distribution of normalized bias and coverage across regression specifications, choice of large language model and prompting strategies.",
    "For each combination of model topic V r, covariate W r, large language model m and prompting strategy p, we randomly sample 5,000 Congressional bills and calculate the plug-in regression coefficient β and the bias-corrected regression coefficient β debiased using a 5% validation sample.",
    "Results are averaged over 1,000 simulations.",
    "See Section 5.4.2 for discussion."
